        "body": "<p><a href=\"http://www.cs.iit.edu/~agam/cs512/lect-notes/opencv-intro/index.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Here<\/a> is an introduction to general OpenCV programming with some useful example programs, including a 'Hello World' .<\/p>\n\n<p>The OpenCV wiki has a <a href=\"http://opencv.willowgarage.com/wiki/Android\" rel=\"noreferrer\">page<\/a> on the Android NDK, a tool to cross-compile OpenCV for the android platform. <\/p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.stanford.edu/~zxwang/android_opencv.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">This<\/a> quick tutorial on OpenCV with Android demonstrates how to use the NDK to cross-compile OpenCV for Android and put together a simple app.<\/p>\n\n<p>That should get you started.<\/p>\n\n<p>Kate.<\/p>\n",
